01:32:22.787 --> 01:32:23.855
See you next Saturday.

01:32:23.955 --> 01:32:25.413
You bet.

01:34:10.686 --> 01:34:12.145
<i>Dear Mr. Vernon.</i>

01:34:13.731 --> 01:34:16.676
<i>We accept the fact that we had to sacrifice
a whole Saturday in detention</i>

01:34:16.776 --> 01:34:18.970
<i>for whatever it was we did wrong</i>

01:34:19.070 --> 01:34:20.972
<i>but we think you're crazy
to make us write an essay</i>

01:34:21.072 --> 01:34:23.057
<i>telling you who we think we are.</i>

01:34:23.157 --> 01:34:25.434
<i>You see us as you want to see us,</i>

01:34:25.534 --> 01:34:29.438
<i>in the simplest terms,
with the most convenient definitions.</i>

01:34:29.538 --> 01:34:33.818
<i>But what we found out is that
each one of us is a brain.</i>

01:34:33.918 --> 01:34:35.486
<i>And an athlete.</i>

01:34:35.586 --> 01:34:37.655
<i>And a basket case.</i>

01:34:37.755 --> 01:34:38.948
<i>A princess.</i>

01:34:39.048 --> 01:34:40.783
<i>And a criminal.</i>

01:34:40.883 --> 01:34:43.828
<i>Does that answer your question?</i>

01:34:43.928 --> 01:34:47.263
<i>Sincerely yours, The Breakfast Club.</i>

